Description:
Walk To Everything!
This immaculate and beautifully maintained near new brick residence is centrally located in a quiet area of Cowes within walking distance to the shops, cafes, RSL, medical complex, school and beach. The comfortable home with a spacious floor plan features a fantastic large living and dining space incorporating the kitchen area including stone bench tops and quality appliances, two good sized bedrooms including the master with spacious ensuite and walk in robe, a family bathroom, separate powder room, laundry and a fabulous enclosed outdoor room with a curved roof. The home is on a fully fenced, low maintenance corner allotment with a lovely landscaped garden. Other great features include split system heating and cooling, ceiling fans, neutral decor, remote control garage, two 2100 litre water tanks, concrete driveway, storage shed and complete with a six star energy rating.
This quality home would be ideal as a permanent residence for first home buyers, couples or retirees and would also appeal to those looking for a low maintenance holiday home in an excellent location.
This property for sale in Cowes, is proudly presented to you by Ray White Real Estate Phillip Island

Description:
OPPORTUNITY KNOCKS ONLY ONCE
Welcome to Fairway Views, the ultimate address for relaxed resort style living.
With the third and final stage currently under construction, now is the time to be part of this gated
community.
Secure a contemporary style townhouse overlooking the second and third fairways of the Phillip Island Golf Course.
There is a choice of three or four bedroom floorplans, all with 2.5 bathrooms, generous living areas,
well-appointed stylish kitchen, alfresco dining area, double garage and fully landscaped gardens.
All townhouses have been designed for luxurious, low maintenance living.
As part of this secure gated complex, residents have access to the swimming pool, tennis court, BBQ hub with full outdoor kitchen and golf putting green.
Located directly opposite Phillip Island golf club and only a short walk to magnificent north facing sandy beaches, this property would make an ideal permanent residence or investment opportunity!
Contact Mike Foenander on 0408 547 677 to secure your investment in this exclusive resort.
Opportunity knocks only once !
Picture yourself here and make the move to start living your dream lifestyle!

Description:
A Fabulous Coastal Escape
This beautiful near new home with a tastefully landscaped native front garden, an easy walk to the Golf Course, park and in close proximity to the north facing beach makes this home ideal for permanent/holiday living or as an investment property.
A lovely tiled entrance leads into a spacious main living, dining and kitchen complimented by stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, fabulous island bench overlooking the family area. Consisting of four bedrooms with built in robes including master with walk in robe and ensuite. The home also offers a family bathroom, including bath, second living area, two car garage and outdoor entertaining area with concrete tiled paving, leading to a large back yard overlooking the wildlife corridor at the rear of the property.
Other great features include: Split system heating and cooling, stone feature wall at front of home, rear access and ample parking for boat/caravan storage, large allotment approx 775 sqm, recycled water for garden use
This property for sale in Cowes, is proudly presented to you by Ray White Real Estate Phillip Island

Description:
STYLISH APARTMENT ON THE COWES FORESHORE
This stylish apartment, located in a quiet and tranquil area in the heart of Cowes, around the corner from north facing foreshore beaches and just a short stroll to fantastic cafes and restaurants.
The apartment has been cleverly designed to take full advantage of the impressive view which extends over the Bay to the shores of Mornington Peninsula. The layout of the apartment provides a spacious open plan living and dining area which extends onto the generous balcony - the perfect place for admiring the view, entertaining friends, or watching the boats pass by out on the Bay. Adjoining the living area is a well-appointed kitchen, complete with island bench, stainless steel appliances and electric oven/cooktop. At the rear of the property, offering privacy and seclusion, are the three bedrooms. The master bedroom features a private balcony and walk through robe leading into the beautiful en-suite with luxurious corner spa bath and separate shower & toilet facilities. The two additional carpeted bedrooms both offer built in robes, with one bedroom providing access to to a spacious rear deck with stylish timber privacy screen, the perfect location for alfresco dining. The main bedroom, with a separate toilet and compact laundry complete the apartment.
Forming part of the Bayview Grande complex, this property provides secure access, lift access to apartment front door, onsite car parking for two vehicles, storage facilities spacious enough for surfboards or fishing gear and access to resort style facilities including indoor heated pool, spa and sauna.
Various furniture items are also available by negotiation.
With its enviable beach-side location and central position, this luxurious apartment would make the perfect holiday or permanent residence. Call to arrange your private inspection.

Description:
Red Rocks Retreat
A family favourite booked all year round with significant repeat business, this fabulous cash flow positive family home is achieving an amazing 10% gross yield on the property asking price, which equates to $70,000 per annum rental income!
Designed to embrace lifestyle and family living is this immaculately presented four bedroom home at the end of a quiet court located within minutes walk to the beautiful north facing Red Rocks Beach and only 200 metres to the Par 3 Golf Course.
Behind double timber gates is a beautiful tree lined, avenue like, driveway leading to a magnificent single level lifestyle property. Boasting a spacious open plan living and well appointed kitchen including a 900mm gas cook top and oven, complimented by stainless steel appliances and stone bench tops. A further large and entirely separate second living/rumpus area makes this the ultimate family home. A large north facing undercover alfresco area flows from both living areas overlooking the north facing lush landscaped garden and childrens playground - perfect for entertaining with family and friends!
The residence comprises four large bedrooms each with ceiling fans, heating and built in robes, master with walk in robe and ensuite, a huge family bathroom with free standing bath, laundry with ample storage and powder room. If this wasn't enough the fantastic holiday rental history boasts a significant return per annum.
Additional features include split system heating/cooling units, walk in showers, double car garage with internal access and loads of storage.
All set on a beautifully landscaped, low maintenance and private fully fenced 910sqm approx allotment and in close proximity to all the Island has to offer, makes this home ideal for permanent/holiday living or as an excellent cashflow positive investment property achieving exceptional 10% gross yield return of approximately $70,000 per annum.
Private Inspections Most Welcome!
